-- Mexico’s Economy Minister Ferrari Continues Recovering
-- B y   J o s e   E n r i q u e   A r r i o j a
-- 2012-11-23T00:12:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-23/mexico-s-economy-minister-ferrari-continues-recovering.html
Mexico Economy Minister Bruno
Ferrari continues his recovery and his health evolves
’positively’, his family said today in an e-mailed statement.  Ferrari is still under medical observation in a private
hospital in Mexico City, his family said. Ferrari was
hospitalized Nov. 20 because of a blood clot in his brain, the
Ministry of Economy said that day in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
